column14: Description

1. As a customer, I am required to add username so that I can login
2. As a customer, I am required to add password so that I can login
3. As a customer, I am required to add full name so that I am recognize by driver and make reservation
4. As a customer, I am required to add contact number so that I can be contacted by driver and staff
5. As a customer, I am required to add email address so that i can receive the latest news and promotion
6. As a customer, I am required to add date of birth so that staff can send me birthday wishes and birthday promotion or voucher.

column14: Allow manager to generate or view reservation monthly summary report by selecting the desire month.
Allow manager to generate or view driver yearly summary report by selecting the desire year.
Allow manager to generate or view reservation monthly summary report by selecting the desire month.
Allow manager to generate or view driver monthly summary report by selecting the desire month.
Allow staff to generate or view customer monthly summary report by selecting the desire month.
Allow manager to generate or view customer yearly summary report by selecting the desire year.
Allow manager to generate or view payment monthly transaction report by selecting the desire days.

1. As a customer, I am required to enter username so that I can login.
2. As a customer, I am required to enter password so that I can login.

1. As a driver, I am required to enter username to login.
2. As a driver, I am required to enter password to login.
Allow manager to generate or view payment yearly summary report by selecting the desire month.

1. As a customer, I am required to enter username and email address so that the system will send the new password through email.
2. As a customer, I am allowed to change password by entering new password so that I can login using new password.

1. As a driver, I am required to enter username and email address so that the system will send the new password through email.
2. As a driver, I am allowed to change password by entering new password so that I can login using new password.
1. As a staff, I am allowed to delete customer record so that i do not allow the customer to login.
